  "text": "Electric vehicles have the potential to provide society with many substantial benefits, including 2 reduction of carbon emissions, improvement of public health, increasing national security, and savings 3 on fuel and maintenance cost [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Despite these benefits, electric 4",
